Package: bolteR
Title: Table top dice success simulator
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Kerry", "Cella", , "Kerry.Cella@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The package aims to show in a relatively crude way the likelihood
  of obtaining certain results based on rolling a number of dice. Many of the
  function are built around the Warhammer 40,000 10 edition mechnics, such as
  wounding a target, a models strength and toughness.
